---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">

  <!-- Meta Tags para SEO y redes sociales -->
  <head>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy policy of GestoFinca, ensuring the protection of your personal data according to GDPR regulations." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Privacy Policy - GestoFinca" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="At GestoFinca, we are committed to protecting your personal data. Read our privacy policy." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/assets/images/og-image.jpg" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Privacy Policy - GestoFinca" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="At GestoFinca, we are committed to protecting your personal data. Read our privacy policy." />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/assets/images/og-image.jpg" />
  </head>

  <article class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto py-8 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-6">
      At <span class="font-semibold">GestoFinca</span>, we are committed to protecting the privacy and personal data of our users. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information in accordance with current legislation in Spain, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the Organic Law on Data Protection and Guarantee of Digital Rights (LOPDGDD).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      <strong>Name:</strong> [Company Name] <br />
      <strong>Address:</strong> [Company Address] <br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> [Contact Email] <br />
      <strong>Phone:</strong> [Phone Number]
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We collect the following personal data:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Contact information: name, email address, phone number.</li>
      <li>Navigation information: IP address, device type, operating system, browser.</li>
      <li>Other data you provide directly through forms or communications.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We use your data to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Provide our services and products.</li>
      <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests.</li>
      <li>Improve our website and personalize your experience.</li>
      <li>Comply with our legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The processing of your data is based on:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Your explicit consent.</li>
      <li>The necessity to process your data for the execution of a contract.</li>
      <li>Compliance with legal obligations.</li>
      <li>Our legitimate interest in improving our services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. User Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Access your personal data.</li>
      <li>Request rectification of inaccurate data.</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your personal data.</li>
      <li>Object to the processing of your data.</li>
      <li>Request restriction of processing your data.</li>
      <li>Port your data to another provider.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-6">
      You can exercise these rights by sending a request to our email:
      <a href="mailto:[Contact Email]" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">[Contact Email]</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Retention Period</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We will retain your personal data for as long as necessary for the purposes described in this privacy policy, unless the law requires or allows a longer retention period.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. International Transfers</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We do not transfer your personal data outside the European Economic Area (EEA). If we do, we will ensure that your data is adequately protected.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">8. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We implement technical and organizational measures to ensure the security of your personal data and prevent unauthorized alteration, loss, access, or processing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We may update this privacy policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted on this page with the date of the latest update.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can contact us at:
      <a href="mailto:[Contact Email]" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">[Contact Email]</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">
      Last updated: <span class="font-semibold">[Last Update Date]</span>
    </p>
  </article>

</Layout>
